trailingComments.value:
*
 * Returns a new list or string with the elements or characters in reverse
 * order.
 *
 * @param {Array|String} list
 * @return {Array|String}
 * @example
 *
 *      reverse([1, 2, 3]);  //=> [3, 2, 1]
 *      reverse([1, 2]);     //=> [2, 1]
 *      reverse([1]);        //=> [1]
 *      reverse([]);         //=> []
 *
 *      reverse('abc');      //=> 'cba'
 *      reverse('ab');       //=> 'ba'
 *      reverse('a');        //=> 'a'
 *      reverse('');         //=> ''
